ct's production time, calculated in seconds.\n[/code]\n\nEach Input corresponds to an ingredient in your recipe. You can create a recipe with just one or two ingredients if you wish. Like this example:\n[code]\n{\n\t\"input1\": {\"acfONE\": [1, 1]},\n\t\"input2\": {\"acfTWO\": [1, 1]}, \n\t\"input3\": {}, \n\t\"outputs\": [\n\t\t{\"item\": [\"acfTHREE\",1], \"chance\": 100}\n\t\t],\n\t\"time\" : 1\n},\n[/code]\n\nYou can also add several output items. \n[code]\n{\n\t\"input1\": {\"acfRED\": [1, 1]},\n\t\"input2\": {\"acfGREEN\": [1, 1]}, \n\t\"input3\": {}, \n\t\"outputs\": [\n\t\t{\"item\": [\"acfYELLOW\",1], \"chance\": 100},\n\t\t{\"item\": [\"acfBLACK\",1], \"chance\": 5}\n\t\t],\n\t\"time\" : 1\n},\n[/code]",
